Package: EraBrewer
Type: Package
Title: Color Palettes from the Album Covers of Each Taylor Swift Era
Version: 0.2.0
URL: https://s-m.ac/EraBrewer/, https://github.com/mathias-sm/EraBrewer
BugReports: https://github.com/mathias-sm/EraBrewer/issues
Authors@R: c(
