Description: Provides discrete and continuous color palettes derived from
    the album cover artwork of each Taylor Swift Era. Each palette
    ships with a curated order-of-use so that smaller discrete subsets
    remain harmonious, and supports continuous interpolation via
    'grDevices::colorRampPalette()' for arbitrary 'n'. Designed to plug
    into 'ggplot2' workflows through standard manual and gradient
    scales.
